Title: CSE 143 Turn-in Policy
Body: Think of this as a roadmap that your TA can use to decipher this stack of paper you're turning in -- something that can be quickly scanned to get an understanding of what's to come (note that if you're well-organized, this can double as your README file, as explained below) code -- your code should be fully commented so that it's clear what each function does: what its preconditions, postconditions, and invariants are.
